rows.label: qst104215_msg0003
rows.name:
A miraculous meeting... No,
did you come looking for me?

rows.label: qst104215_msg0007
rows.name:
The paths connecting the
islands look like roots.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0008
rows.name:
Alright, I'll be a teacher. But
only after I finish my work.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0009
rows.name:
If you find the precious
root in Spirit Crucible
Elpys for me, I'll go.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0061
rows.name:
I want a Colla Carrot from the secret
area in Spirit Crucible Elpys.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0062
rows.name:
A villager told me not to go
alone because of the monsters.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0063
rows.name:
You all should be fine,
though. I'm counting on you.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0121
rows.name: The secret area is a beautiful lake.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0122
rows.name:
Remember, a Colla Carrot. It's
a root. Don't get it wrong.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0151
rows.name:
A Colla Carrot! Alright, I've
decided to be a teacher.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0152
rows.name:
I'll return to the clinic in
Superbia, and once I'm ready,
I'll head to Iyasaki Village.
